[Quotes]
victory0 = "I was expecting a battle, not a tantrum from a child. Are you even trying?"
victory1 = "This is the end for you, my friend. You have my condolences."
victory2 = "I'm afraid your pitiful resistance ends here."
victory3 = "Now you see the true terror that is Frieza!"
victory4 = "I told you, didn't I? There's no point in resisting."
victory5 = "Do you understand now? The gap between us is... insurmountable."
victory6 = "Another corpse to add to my collection. How boring."
victory7 = "Was that truly your best? How very... disappointing."
victory8 = "You fought like an insect. And like one, you've been crushed."
victory9 = "Try not to feel too ashamed. Even the mightiest fall before me."
victory10 = "You never had a chance. But I appreciate the effort... it made this mildly entertaining."
victory11 = "Victory was inevitable. You were simply too slow to realize it."
victory12 = "I suppose I'll leave just enough of you for someone to mourn."
victory13 = "Is that all? What a dreadful disappointment."
victory14 = "You are like a mosquito to me. No... that's too generous."
victory15 = "Kneel? Oh, you don't have knees anymore... how unfortunate."
victory16 = "I've reduced entire civilizations to ash for less. You should feel honored."
victory17 = "I wonder... did your family hear that final scream?"


